'''皈依者狂热'''描述了对新信仰的强烈推崇并与旧信仰坚决划清界限的一种信徒现象。<ref name="PewResearchCenter">{{cite web | url=https://www.pewforum.org/2009/10/28/the-zeal-of-the-convert-is-it-the-real-deal/ | website=Pew Research Center | title=The “Zeal of the Convert”: Is It the Real Deal? |language=en| date=2009-10-28|access-date=2021-03-10|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310160456/https://www.pewforum.org/2009/10/28/the-zeal-of-the-convert-is-it-the-real-deal/|archive-date=2021-03-10}}</ref><ref name="WileyOnlineLibrary">{{cite web | url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/jssr.12698 |language=en| title=The Zeal of the Convert Revisited|author=Nadia Beider|website=Wiley Online Library| date=2020-12-06|access-date=2020-03-10|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310161500/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/jssr.12698|archive-date=2020-03-10}}</ref><ref name="ScholarWorksAtGeorgiaStateUniversity">{{cite web|url=https://scholarworks.gsu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1198&context=psych_theses|title=Zeal of the Convert? Comparing the Structure of Islamic Religiousness between Convert and Non-Convert Muslims|language=en|website=ScholarWorks @ Georgia State University|author=Daniel Snook|date=2019-05-01|access-date=2021-03-10|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027154742/https://scholarworks.gsu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1198&context=psych_theses|archive-date=2020-10-27}}</ref>

== 用法 ==
“皈依者狂热”常在民间使用于改变信仰的狂热者，因为他们常常表现出比原信仰者更强烈的信仰。<ref name="ScholarWorksAtGeorgiaStateUniversity" />

== 例子 ==
哈立德·马苏德（Khalid Masood）皈依后在[[西敏宫|西敏宫]]外杀了4人。<ref name="economist">{{cite web|url=https://www.economist.com/britain/2017/04/01/converts-to-islam-are-likelier-to-radicalise-than-native-muslims|title=Converts to Islam are likelier to radicalise than native Muslims|date=2017-04-01|access-date=2021-03-10|website=The Economist|language=en|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429144524/https://www.economist.com/britain/2017/04/01/converts-to-islam-are-likelier-to-radicalise-than-native-muslims|archive-date=2021-04-29}}</ref>

